"{\"uid\": \"nbcsports.com-pressbox-olympics-press-releases-gold-zone-whip-around-show-makes-peacock-debut-during-nbcuniversals-coverage-of-olympic-games-paris-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Gold Zone to Guide Viewers to the Best and Most Exciting Live Moments During Paris 2024  Hanson to Open Each Day's Coverage, Followed by Siciliano, with Iseman and Gbajabiamila Co-Hosting Day's Concluding Coverage; Special Guests to Join Hosts Often Throughout the Day  STAMFORD, Conn. - March 20, 2024 - Scott Hanson,Andrew Siciliano,Matt IsemanandAkbar Gbajabiamilawill serve as hosts of theGold Zonewhip-around show, which will stream for the first time live on Peacock during NBCUniversal's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 2024.Gold Zonewill stream live on Peacock from 7 am - 5 pm ET each day from July 27-Aug. 10.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 625, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 79, \"end\": 89, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.2694218541170685e-13, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 272, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"score\": 0.9999322658457888, \"rank\": 6.773874206871506e-05, \"text\": \"STAMFORD\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stamford_Transportation_Center\"}, {\"begin\": 482, \"end\": 494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 0.9511421124884083, \"rank\": 0.05136758580490682, \"text\": \"NBCUniversal\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 567, \"end\": 574, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999984074748, \"rank\": 1.577623738665919e-09, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The announcement was made byMolly Solomon, Executive Producer and President, NBC Olympics Production.\", \"from\": 626, \"to\": 727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 669, \"end\": 687, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Executive_producer\", \"score\": 0.999995292599517, \"rank\": 4.705826452010305e-06, \"text\": \"Executive Producer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Executive_producer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Executive_producer\"}, {\"begin\": 703, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBC Olympics\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Olympic_broadcasts\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With up to 40 events happening simultaneously during the Paris Olympic Games,Gold Zonewill present viewers with the best and most compelling moments happening at any time.\", \"from\": 729, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The daily live show will guide fans through the excitement, triumphs, and emotion of the Games, scanning all the events that day to provide viewers with the most exhilarating moments and key races, routines, and finishes as they unfold live.Gold Zone's daily offering will provide viewers with the most comprehensive and all-encompassing live whip-around coverage of any Olympic Games to date.\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympic Games are like no other sporting event with up to 40 competitions happening simultaneously.\", \"from\": 1296, \"to\": 1400, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Given that scale,Gold Zoneis designed to be the viewer's best friend, streaming the most important moments in real time,\\\" said Solomon.\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Never miss a moment or a medal withGold Zone, and who better to guide viewers through this entertaining presentation than Scott Hanson, who does this every NFL weekend, and Olympic veterans Andrew Siciliano, Matt Iseman and Akbar Gbajabiamila.\\\"\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1660, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Scott Hanson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Scott_Hanson\"}, {\"begin\": 1728, \"end\": 1744, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andrew Siciliano\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrew_Siciliano\"}, {\"begin\": 1746, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Iseman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Iseman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Iseman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Iseman\"}, {\"begin\": 1762, \"end\": 1780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akbar_Gbaja-Biamila\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Akbar Gbajabiamila\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q14128148\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akbar_Gbaja-Biamila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Akbar_Gbaja-Biamila\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hanson, the celebrated host ofNFL RedZone, will open each day's coverage on Peacock.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1868, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999984074748, \"rank\": 1.577623738665919e-09, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has served as the host ofNFL RedZonesince its inaugural season in 2009, taking viewers through every touchdown and exciting moment live on Sunday afternoons to critical acclaim.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 2049, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He also is a host of NFL Network's on-location coverage of events, including the Super Bowl, NFL Draft, and more.\", \"from\": 2050, \"to\": 2163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2143, \"end\": 2146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"score\": 0.9867991799893187, \"rank\": 0.013350718286963381, \"text\": \"NFL\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_on_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This will be Hanson's first Olympic assignment.\", \"from\": 2164, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2177, \"end\": 2183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 3.286647438695328e-13, \"text\": \"Hanson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tommy_Hanson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Siciliano, a host and play-by-play announcer for NFL Network and host of the groundbreakingRed Zone Channelon DIRECTVfrom 2005-2022, will also hostGold Zonehosting duties following Hanson each day.\", \"from\": 2213, \"to\": 2410, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2262, \"end\": 2273, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_Network\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.73729447453641e-14, \"text\": \"NFL Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NFL_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \