g/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Iseman, working his third Olympics with NBC Sports, and Gbajabiamila, in his second Olympics, served as hosts of Peacock's Tokyo Olympics morning show,Tokyo Live, in 2021.\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2839, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2708, \"end\": 2718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.7715314163862371, \"rank\": 0.2961217222205679, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}, {\"begin\": 2781, \"end\": 2788, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999984074748, \"rank\": 1.577623738665919e-09, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Iseman was also a host on Peacock's coverage of the Beijing Olympics in 2022.\", \"from\": 2840, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2866, \"end\": 2873, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"score\": 0.9999999984074748, \"rank\": 1.577623738665919e-09, \"text\": \"Peacock\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peafowl\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gbajabiamila is co-host ofThe Talk.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The hosts will often be joined by special guests throughout the day.\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 3023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Additional hosts and programming details for NBCU's Paris Olympics'Gold Zoneprogram will be announced soon.Gold Zonewill also be available on NBCSports.com and the NBC Sports app via \\\"TV Everywhere\\\" for customers with pay-TV subscriptions.\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3263, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3069, \"end\": 3073, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCU\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCUniversal\"}, {\"begin\": 3076, \"end\": 3081, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999857650438, \"rank\": 1.4234882154374804e-08, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 3166, \"end\": 3179, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"NBCSports.com\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 3188, \"end\": 3198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.7715314163862371, \"rank\": 0.2961217222205679, \"text\": \"NBC Sports\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Peacock will be the streaming home of the 2024 Paris Olympics, providing fans with the most comprehensive Olympic destination in U.S. media history.\", \"from\": 3265, \"to\": 3413, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In a Summer Games first for Peacock, it will stream every sport and event, including all 329 medal events, and will feature full-event replays; all NBC programming; curated video clips; virtual channels; exclusive original programming; and more.\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3562, \"end\": 3565, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.7813562020134642, \"rank\": 0.2793074273481119, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more on NBCU's coverage of the Olympic Games Paris 202